spec_data.Name: texlive-baskervaldx
spec_data.Description:
Extends and modifies the BaskervaldADF font (a Baskerville
substitute) with more accented glyphs, with small caps and
oldstyle figures in all shapes. Includes OpenType and
PostScript fonts, as well as LaTeX support files.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:11:14 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Extension and modification of BaskervaldADF with LaTeX support
